    <header id="home">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1 class="hero-title">
                THAT <span class="text-neon">GREEN DAY</span> BAND
            </h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">The world's #1 Green Day tribute band<br />since 2008!</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="about">
            <div class="bio-grid">
                <div class="bio-image">
                    <img src="group-shot.png" alt="That Green Day Band" style="width: 100%; display: block;">
                </div>
                <div class="bio-text glass-panel">
                    <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 2rem;">LOUD & <span class="text-neon">FAST</span></h2>
                    <p>That Green Day Band doesn't just play the songs. They bring the chaotic, high-voltage energy of early 90s punk back to the stage.</p>
                    <p>Focusing on the entire Green Day catalog from <em>Kerplunk!</em> to <em>Saviors</em> and everything in-between, TGDB strips away the bloat and delivers the raw anthems that defined a generation.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="shows">
            <h2 class="section-title text-outline">LIVE CONCERTS</h2>
            <div class="glass-panel">
                <div class="show-list">
                    
                    <!-- SHOW ITEM START -->
                    <div class="show-item">
                        <div class="show-date">JUN 20</div>
                        <div class="show-venue">
                            Tailgaters
                            <div class="show-location">Bolingbrook, IL</div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- We changed href="#" to an onclick event -->
                        <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="show-btn" onclick="openModal('Tailgaters Sports Bar', 'June 20th, 2026', 'DOORS: 7PM / SHOW: 9PM', '431 W Boughton Road', 'Bolingbrook, IL 60440', '(630) 679-1994', 'w/ Chart Attack!!')">Details</a>
                    </div>
                    <!-- SHOW ITEM END -->

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

